create a folder called font

inside this folder create a file called ttf_fonts.css
copy this inside the file ttf_fonts.css

'''
@font-face{
  font-family: 'led_digital_7_mono';
  src: url('digital-7/digital-7_mono.ttf');
}
'''


copy contents of led_digital_7 from https://www.fontget.com/font/led-digital-7-family/
inside a folder called digital-7

in Information - EJSS Run options - CSS Files: add the folder ./font/ttf_fonts.css
User files: add ./font/

In Variables defined
fontdigitalmonosmall = "normal normal 3vw led_digital_7_mono"
fontdigitalmono = "normal normal 7vw led_digital_7_mono"
